ime.",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_desc2:"Create entertaining videos with your products just a tap away. Shop Page",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_desc3:"Display your products on a centralized marketplace within TikTok.",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_desc4:"Display your products on a centralized marketplace within TikTok.",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_title1:"LIVE shopping",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_title2:"Shoppable videos",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_title3:"Shop Page",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_title4:"Shop Tab",tts_shop_download_download_button2:"Download app",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc1:"Curated content from a community that makes shopping personalized",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc2:"Everything your fave brands and creators are loving right now, with entertaining LIVEs",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc3:"Scrolling and shopping all in one place \u2014 no need to leave the platform",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc4:"Great value on trending and unique products you'll love",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc5:"Verified sellers, secure payments, and robust safeguards ensure every transaction is worry-free",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc6:"Services like trusted payments, free returns, and free shipping make your shopping experience hassle-free",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title1:"Recs from people just like you",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title2:"Inspiring shoppable LIVE content",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title3:"Seamless shopping all on TikTok",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title4:"Quality products for less",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title5:"Secure shopping with confidence",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title6:"Service that doesn't stop at the sale",tts_shop_download_title2_h1:"Discover, Scroll, Shop \u2014 All in One Place",tts_shop_download_title2_h2:"This is where a world of discovery meets joyful shopping \u2014 all on TikTok. Every swipe brings the chance to uncover something new, unique, and unexpected, inspired by the community you love.",tts_shop_download_title3_h1:"A shopping experience just for you",tts_shop_download_title3_h2:"Through a seamless suite of in-app shopping features, TikTok Shop empowers brands and creators to showcase and sell products directly on TikTok \u2014 turning discovery into shopping",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Delivery_guarantee:"Delivery guarantee",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Delivery_guarantee_content:"Get automatically refunded if your package is reported as lost or damaged by the carrier.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds:"Easy returns and refunds",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds_content1:"Free returns on most items for 30 days",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds_content2:"Easy dropoffs at UPS, USPS, FedEx, or Walgreens",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds_content3:"No box/label required at UPS, simply scan the QR code",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds_content4:"Instant refunds at dropoff for qualifying returns",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content1:"TikTok Shop uses highly secure payment methods. Transactions are fully encrypted and regulated by the Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard (PCI DSS)",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content2:"We never share payment information with sellers",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content3:"We accept the following payment methods:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content4:"Security certifications:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content1:"We are committed to protecting your privacy. Multiple safeguards secure your data, and we will never share or sell your information without your consent.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content2:"View TikTok Shop's <link>Privacy Policy</link> to understand your rights, data security methods, and use of any information.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content3:"Need help? Our virtual help center is available within the TikTok app 24/7, and our live agents are ready to assist you during business hours.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_learn_more:"Learn more",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_money_back_guarantee_content:"Our coverage is completely free and automatic on eligible orders for up to 90 days - if your item arrives damaged or defective. Limitations and exclusions apply.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_secure_payments_content5:"To use any of the payment options below, please make your purchase in-app:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_subtitle:"We're committed to giving you a great shopping experience.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle1:"Secure payments",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle2:"Money-back guarantee",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle4:"24/7 in-app support",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle5:"Data privacy",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_title:"TikTok Shop protections",tts_shop_returns_module_logged_out_content:"Most items are eligible for <b>free returns within 30 days of delivery</b> for a refund. Some items, including ingestibles, hygiene products, and pre-owned goods, are non-returnable. Final sale items cannot be returned or replaced. <b>Please log in to view this item's specific return policy.</b>",tts_shop_returns_module_title:"Returns made easy",tts_shop_shipping_module_logged_out_content:"Many items qualify for free shipping or become eligible once the order threshold is met.",tts_shop_shipping_module_title:"Shipping & delivery",tts_web_seo_coupon_center_bottom_title:"Get up to $100 in coupon center",tts_web_seo_coupon_center_pdp_login_coupon_title1:"Log in to check your coupons",tts_web_seo_coupon_center_pdp_login_coupon_title2:"V