ndu(s)",ecom_free_sample_product_promote_page_cta_details:"D\xe9tails",ecom_pdp_logistics_ship_fee_sbs:"Livraison \xe0 {f_cost} sur cette commande",ecom_promotion_couponsandpromotion_intromessage:"R\xe9cup\xe8re ces coupons et ils seront appliqu\xe9s automatiquement au moment du paiement. \nTu peux appliquer 1\xa0coupon et/ou promotion TikTok Shop et 1\xa0coupon et/ou promotion de chaque vendeur. Des conditions individuelles s'appliquent.",ecom_select_address_confirm_button:"Confirmer",ecom_shop_logout_button:"D\xe9connexion",ecom_shop_search_filter_button_show_results:"Afficher les r\xe9sultats",ecom_view_all:"Tout afficher",ecom_view_cart:"Voir le panier",pdp_sps_24h_response_rate:"Taux de r\xe9ponse\nen 24\xa0h",pdp_sps_positive_feedback:"Avis positifs",pdp_store_reviews_from_this_shop:"Avis sur la boutique",sea_creator_crm_filters:"Filtres",search_button:"Rechercher",seo_pdp_peopleSearchedFor:"Autres recherches populaires",seo_pdp_shop_waist_entrance_sold:"Vendu(s)",seo_us_deals_endsin:"Prend fin dans",shop_about_seller_info_header:"Informations relatives au vendeur",shop_order_shipping_options_header:"Livraison gratuite",shop_page_info_business_name:"Nom de l'entreprise",store_seller_address:"Adresse de l'entreprise",ttec_pdp_us_shipping_and_return:"Livraison et retours",tts_information_buyer_policy:"Politique des clients",tts_information_final_sales:"Vente d\xe9finitive",tts_information_return_policy:"Politique de retour",tts_information_tts_protections:"Protections de TikTok\xa0Shop",tts_pdp_title_more_from:"Explorer plus en d\xe9tail chez {s_shopName}",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_desc1:"Mets tes produits en avant, vends-les et interagis avec ton public en temps r\xe9el.",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_desc2:"Cr\xe9e des vid\xe9os divertissantes avec tes produits en un rien de temps. Page Boutique",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_desc3:"Affiche tes produits sur un march\xe9 centralis\xe9 au sein de TikTok.",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_desc4:"Affiche tes produits sur un march\xe9 centralis\xe9 au sein de TikTok.",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_title1:"Achats LIVE",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_title2:"Vid\xe9os shopping",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_title3:"Page Boutique",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_title4:"Onglet Boutique",tts_shop_download_download_button2:"T\xe9l\xe9charger l'application",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc1:"Du contenu adapt\xe9 d'une communaut\xe9 qui rend l'exp\xe9rience d'achat unique",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc2:"Tout ce que tes marques et tes cr\xe9ateurs pr\xe9f\xe9r\xe9s adorent en ce moment, accompagn\xe9 de LIVE qui vont te plaire",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc3:"Scrolle et ach\xe8te sur la m\xeame plateforme",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc4:"Prix avantageux pour des produits uniques et tendance que tu vas adorer",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc5:"Des vendeurs v\xe9rifi\xe9s, des paiements s\xe9curis\xe9s et des mesures de s\xe9curit\xe9 robustes garantissent des transactions sans souci",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc6:"Des services comme les paiements s\xe9curis\xe9s, les retours gratuits et la livraison gratuite simplifient ton exp\xe9rience d\u2019achat",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title1:"Recommandations de personnes comme toi",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title2:"Contenu LIVE shopping inspirant",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title3:"Acheter en tout simplicit\xe9 sur TikTok",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title4:"Des produits de qualit\xe9 \xe0 moindre co\xfbt",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title5:"Des achats en toute s\xe9curit\xe9",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title6:"Service qui continue au-del\xe0 de la vente",tts_shop_download_title2_h1:"D\xe9couvre, scrolle, ach\xe8te. Le tout au m\xeame endroit",tts_shop_download_title2_h2:"TikTok\xa0: un monde o\xf9 les d\xe9couvertes et les achats se marient \xe0 merveille. Derri\xe8re chaque swipe se cache quelque chose de nouveau, d\u2019unique et d\u2019inattendu, inspir\xe9 par la communaut\xe9 que tu aimes.",tts_shop_download_title3_h1:"Une exp\xe9rience d'achat, juste pour toi",tts_shop_download_title3_h2:"Gr\xe2ce \xe0 une gamme de fonctionnalit\xe9s d'achat parfaitement int\xe9gr\xe9es, TikTok Shop permet aux marques et aux cr\xe9ateurs de pr\xe9senter et de vendre leurs produits directement sur TikTok, transformant la d\xe9couverte en exp\xe9rience d'achat",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Delivery_guarantee:"Garantie de livraison",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Delivery_guarantee_content:"Obtiens automatiquement un remboursement si ton colis est perdu ou endommag\xe9 par le transporteur.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds:"Retours et remboursements faciles",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds_content1:"Retours gratuits sur la plupart des articles pendant 30\xa0jours",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds_content2:"D\xe9p\xf4ts faciles avec UPS, USPS, FedEx ou Walgreens",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds_content3:"Aucun emballage/\xe9tiquette requis chez UPS, il te suffit de scanner le code QR",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds_content4:"Remboursements instantan\xe9s au moment du d\xe9p\xf4t pour les retours \xe9ligibles",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content1:"TikTok Shop utilise des m\xe9thodes de paiement hautement s\xe9curis\xe9es. Les transactions sont enti\xe8rement chiffr\xe9es et r\xe9gies par la norme de s\xe9curit\xe9 des donn\xe9es de l'industrie des cartes de paiement (PCI DSS).",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content2:"Nous ne partageons jamais les informations de paiement avec les vendeurs ",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content3:"Nous acceptons les modes de paiement suivants\xa0:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content4:"Certifications de s\xe9curit\xe9\xa0:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content1:"Nous nous engageons \xe0 prot\xe9ger ta vie priv\xe9e. Plusieurs garanties sont mises en place pour prot\xe9ger tes donn\xe9es et nous ne partagerons ni ne vendrons jamais tes informations sans ton consentement.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content2:"Consulte la Politique de confidentialit\xe9 de TikTok Shop pour comprendre tes droits, les m\xe9thodes de s\xe9curit\xe9 des donn\xe9es utilis\xe9es et l'usage qui est fait de tes informations.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content3:"Besoin d'aide\xa0? Notre centre d'aide virtuel est disponible 24\xa0heures sur\xa024 et 7\xa0jours sur\xa07 sur l'application TikTok, et nos agents en ligne sont pr\xeats \xe0 t'assister pendant les heures d'ouverture du centre d'aide.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_learn_more:"En savoir plus",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_money_back_guarantee_content:"Notre couverture est enti\xe8rement gratuite et automatique sur les commandes \xe9ligibles jusqu'\xe0 90\xa0jours - si ton article arrive endommag\xe9 ou d\xe9fectueux. Des limitations et des exclusions s'appliquent.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_secure_payments_content5:"Pour utiliser l'une des options de paiement ci-dessous, effectue ton achat au sein de l'application\xa0:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_subtitle:"Nous nous engageons \xe0 t'offrir une exp\xe9rience d'achat exceptionnelle.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle1:"Paiements s\xe9curis\xe9s",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle2:"Garantie de remboursement",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle4:"Assistance client 24\xa0h/24, 7\xa0j/7 dans l'application",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle5:"Confidentialit\xe9 des donn\xe9es",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_title:"Protections de TikTok\xa0Shop",tts_shop_returns_module_logged_out_content:"La plupart des articles sont \xe9ligibles \xe0 un <b>retour gratuit dans les 30\xa0jours suivant la livraison</b> afin d'obtenir un remboursement. Certains articles, notamment les produits alimentaires, les produits d'hygi\xe8ne et les produits de seconde main, ne peuvent pas faire l'objet d'un retour. Les articles ni repris ni \xe9chang\xe9s ne sont pas \xe9ligibles \xe0 un retour ou un remplacement.",tts_shop_returns_module_title:"Retours simplifi\xe9s",tts_shop_shipping_module_logged_out_content:"De nombreux articles sont \xe9ligibles \xe0 la livraison gratuite ou le deviennent lorsqu'un certain seuil de commande est atteint.",tts_shop_shipping_module_title:"Exp\xe9dition et livraison",tts_web_seo_coupon_center_bottom_title:"Get up to $100 in coupon center",tts_web_seo_coupon_center_pdp_login_coupon_title1:"Log in to check your coupons",tts_web_seo_coupon_center_pdp_login_coupon_title2:"View and claim any available offers once you're logged in.",tts_web_seo_coupon_center_pdp_no_coupon_title:"Sorry, none of your coupons apply to this specific product. You can tap \u201CSee All\u201D to view all available coupons in TikTok Shop.",tts_web_seo_pdp_review_count:"Affichage de {total_reviews}\xa0avis sur {review_count}",tts_web_seo_pdp_review_filter:"Filtrer par",tts_web_seo_pdp_review_filter_all:"Tous",tts_web_seo_pdp_review_filter_reset:"R\xe9initialiser les filtres",tts_web_seo_pdp_review_filter_verified:"Achat v\xe9rifi\xe9",tts_web_seo_pdp_review_filter_visuals:"Avec photos",tts_web_seo_pdp_review_sku:"Article",tts_web_seo_pdp_review_sort_recent:"Plus r\xe9cent",tts_web_seo_pdp_review_sort_recommended:"Recommandation",ug_paid_ads_seo_Shop_BR:"TikTok Shop Brazil",ug_paid_ads_seo_Shop_MX:"TikTok Shop M\xe9xico",ug_paid_ads_seo_Shop_Tokopedia:"Shop | Tokopedia",ug_paid_ads_seo_TikTok_Shop_Malaysia:"TikTok\xa0Shop Malaysia",ug_paid_ads_seo_TikTok_Shop_Philippines:"TikTok\xa0Shop Philippines",ug_paid_ads_seo_TikTok_Shop_Singapore:"TikTok\xa0Shop Singapore",ug_paid_ads_seo_TikTok_Shop_Thailand:"TikTok\xa0Shop Thailand",ug_paid_ads_seo_TikTok_Shop_UK:"TikTok\xa0Shop UK",ug_paid_ads_seo_TikTok_Shop_US:"TikTok Shop",ug_paid_ads_seo_TikTok_Shop_Vietnam:"TikTok\xa0Shop Vietnam",ug_paid_ads_seo_about_this_product:"\xc0 propos de ce produit",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_affiliate:"Affiliation",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_buy:"Acheter",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_buy_promo_code:"Codes promo",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_buy_website:"Sites web mondiaux TikTok Shop",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_careers:"Carri\xe8res",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_community_guidelines:"R\xe8gles de la communaut\xe9",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_company_info:"\xc0 propos de",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_contact_us:"Nous contacter",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_customer_service:"Assistance client",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_freeshipping:"Livraison gratuite",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_make_money_with_us:"Vendre",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_new_customer_discount:"Offres pour les nouveaux clients",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_policy_legal:"Mentions l\xe9gales",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_privacy_policy:"Politique de confidentialit\xe9",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_seller_center:"Centre des vendeurs",ug_paid_ads_seo_footer_terms_of_service:"Conditions de service",ug_paid_ads_seo_homepage_logo:"Logo de la page d'accueil {TikTok_shop_country}",ug_paid_ads_seo_logo:"Logo {TikTok_shop_country}",ug_paid_ads_seo_newuser_coupon_requirement:"Aucun minimum de d\xe9pense sur les produits \xe9ligibles",ug_paid_ads_seo_newuser_coupon_title1:"Coupon pour les nouveaux clients",ug_paid_ads_seo_newuser_coupon_title2:"V\xe9rifier dans l'application. Les crit\xe8res d'\xe9ligibilit\xe9 peuvent varier",ug_paid_ads_seo_openapp:"Ouvrir l'application","ug_paid_ads_seo_pc_global reviews":"{review_count_str}\xa0avis mondiaux",ug_paid_ads_seo_pc_load_more:"Voir plus",ug_paid_ads_seo_pdp_description_new:"Ach\xe8te {product_name} sur {TikTok_shop_country}. D\xe9couvre nos tarifs exceptionnels sur la cat\xe9gorie {cate_name} et profite de la livraison gratuite sur les articles \xe9ligibles. Fais ton shopping pour d\xe9couvrir nos bonnes affaires exclusives\xa0!",ug_paid_ads_seo_pdp_popup_button:"Ouvrir TikTok",ug_paid_ads_seo_pdp_popup_cancel:"Pas maintenant",ug_paid_ads_seo_pdp_popup_description:"D\xe9couvre plus de produits et de fonctionnalit\xe9s int\xe9ressantes sur l'application.",ug_paid_ads_seo_pdp_popup_title:"Profite de l'exp\xe9rience compl\xe8te avec l'application",ug_paid_ads_seo_pdp_video_for_this_product:"Vid\xe9os pour ce produit",ug_paid_ads_seo_review_medias_from_reviews:"Photos provenant des avis",ug_paid_ads_seo_sea_kep_popup_window_title:"Profite de l'exp\xe9rience compl\xe8te sur l'application",ug_paid_ads_seo_search_tab_title:"Trending search",ug_paid_ads_seo_tiktokshop_desc:"D\xe9couverte e-commerce",web2app_landingpage_count_down_da_plural:"jours"}},"fr-FR":{},it:{SEO:{Product_list_end:"Non ci sono altri prodotti",Show_window_change_cover_image_confirm:"Conferma",ec_center_learn_from_creators_live_detail_page_reset_button:"Reimposta",ec_liveroom_coupon_countdown:"Scade tra {{s_countdown}}",ec_order_details_see_more:"Vedi altro",ec_order_details_view_more:"Visualizza altro",ec_pdp_btn_buy:"Acquista subito",ec_pdp_btn_cart:"Aggiungi al carrello",ec_pdp_detail:"Descrizione del prodotto",ec_pdp_error_server_desc:"Riprova.",ec_pdp_error_server_tle:"Si \xe8 verificato un problema",ec_pdp_net_btn:"Riprova",ec_pdp_net_desc:"Connettiti a internet e riprova.",ec_pdp_quantity:"Quantit\xe0",ec_pdp_safety:"Sicurezza e conformit\xe0",ec_pdp_sold:"%s venduti",ec_pdp_sold_out:"Esaurito",ec_pdp_variation:"Opzioni di selezione",ec_shop_pdp_pdt_region_error_title:"Prodotto non disponibile nella tua nazione o area",ec_shop_review_write_pic_btn_cancel:"Annulla",ecom_PDP_compliance_warning_warning:"AVVERTENZA",ecom_added_to_cart:"Aggiunto al carrello",ecom_addproduct_recommend_title:"Potrebbe piacerti anche",ecom_checkout_U20_age_gate_confirm_popup_title:"Avviso sui limiti di et\xe0",ecom_checkout_age_gate_purchase_partical_restriction_toast:"Non disponibile per limiti di et\xe0",ecom_coupon_tc:"Termini e condizioni",ecom_creator_contact_info_onboard_dialog_cta_secondary:"Non ora",ecom_customer_reviews:"Recensioni dei clienti",ecom_feedscard_salesvolume:"venduti",ecom_free_sample_product_promote_page_cta_details:"Dettagli",ecom_pdp_logistics_ship_fee_sbs:"{f_cost} di spedizione su questo ordine",ecom_promotion_couponsandpromotion_intromessage:"Riscuoti questi coupon e verranno applicati automaticamente al checkout. \n Puoi utilizzare al massimo 1 coupon e/o sconto di TikTok Shop e 1 coupon e/o sconto offerto dal venditore. Termini e condizioni individuali.",ecom_select_address_confirm_button:"Conferma",ecom_shop_logout_button:"Esci",ecom_shop_search_filter_button_show_results:"Mostra risultati",ecom_view_all:"Visualizza tutti",ecom_view_cart:"Visualizza carrello",pdp_sps_24h_response_rate:"Tasso di risposta nelle 24 ore",pdp_sps_positive_feedback:"Feedback positivo",pdp_store_reviews_from_this_shop:"Recensione del negozio",sea_creator_crm_filters:"Filtri",search_button:"Cerca",seo_pdp_peopleSearchedFor:"Le persone hanno cercato anche",seo_pdp_shop_waist_entrance_sold:"Venduti",seo_us_deals_endsin:"Termina fra",shop_about_seller_info_header:"Informazioni sul venditore",shop_order_shipping_options_header:"Spedizione gratuita",shop_page_info_business_name:"Nome dell'azienda",store_seller_address:"Indirizzo dell'azienda",ttec_pdp_us_shipping_and_return:"Spedizione e resi",tts_information_buyer_policy:"Politica sugli acquirenti",tts_information_final_sales:"Vendita finale",tts_information_return_policy:"Politica sui resi",tts_information_tts_protections:"Protezioni TikTok Shop",tts_pdp_title_more_from:"Esplora altro da {s_shopName}",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_desc1:"Promuovi, vendi e coinvolgi il tuo pubblico, tutto in tempo reale.",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_desc2:"Crea video coinvolgenti con i tuoi prodotti con un semplice tocco. Pagina Negozio",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_desc3:"Mostra i tuoi prodotti in un marketplace centralizzato all'interno di TikTok.",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_desc4:"Mostra i tuoi prodotti in un marketplace centralizzato all'interno di TikTok.",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_title1:"Acquisti tramite LIVE",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_title2:"Video con prodotti acquistabili",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_title3:"Pagina Negozio",tts_shop_download_app_selling_point_title4:"Scheda Negozio",tts_shop_download_download_button2:"Scarica l'app",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc1:"Contenuti elaborati da una community che rende lo shopping personalizzato",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc2:"Tutto ci\xf2 che i tuoi brand e creator preferiti amano in questo momento, all'interno di dirette LIVE coinvolgenti",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc3:"Scorri e acquista in una sola posizione, senza uscire dalla piattaforma",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc4:"Grandi affari su prodotti unici e di tendenza che amerai",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc5:"Venditori verificati, pagamenti protetti e solide misure di sicurezza permettono di effettuare transazioni senza preoccupazioni",tts_shop_download_selling_point_desc6:"Servizi come pagamenti sicuri, resi gratuiti e spedizione gratuita rendono il tuo shopping un'esperienza rilassante",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title1:"I consigli di persone come te",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title2:"Contenuto ispirante nella LIVE con prodotti acquistabili",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title3:"Shopping senza pensieri su TikTok",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title4:"Prodotti di qualit\xe0 a prezzi pi\xf9 bassi",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title5:"Acquista con fiducia e con la massima protezione",tts_shop_download_selling_point_title6:"Un servizio non limitato alla sola vendita",tts_shop_download_title2_h1:"Scopri, scorri, acquista, tutto in un solo punto",tts_shop_download_title2_h2:"Un mondo di scoperte incontra la gioia dello shopping. Tutto su TikTok. Ogni selezione ti offre la possibilit\xe0 di scoprire qualcosa di nuovo, unico e inaspettato, ispirato dalla community che ami.",tts_shop_download_title3_h1:"Un'esperienza di shopping fatta per te",tts_shop_download_title3_h2:"Grazie a una suite di funzionalit\xe0 di shopping in-app, TikTok Shop consente a brand e creator di mostrare e vendere i prodotti direttamente su TikTok, trasformando la scoperta in acquisto",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Delivery_guarantee:"Garanzia di consegna",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Delivery_guarantee_content:"Ricevi automaticamente il rimborso se il tuo pacco viene segnalato come smarrito o danneggiato dal corriere.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds:"Resi e rimborsi facili",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds_content1:"Resi gratuiti sulla maggior parte degli articoli per 30 giorni",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds_content2:"Consegne facili a UPS, USPS, FedEx o Walgreens",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds_content3:"Nessuna scatola/etichetta richiesta presso UPS: scansiona semplicemente il codice QR",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Easy_returns_and_refunds_content4:"Rimborsi istantanei alla consegna per resi qualificati",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content1:"TikTok Shop utilizza metodi di pagamento altamente sicuri. Le transazioni sono completamente criptate e regolate dal Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard (PCI DSS)",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content2:"Non condividiamo mai le informazioni di pagamento con i venditori",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content3:"Accettiamo i seguenti metodi di pagamento:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content4:"Certificazioni di sicurezza:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content1:"Ci impegniamo a proteggere la tua privacy. Molteplici misure di sicurezza tengono al sicuro i tuoi dati e non condivideremo o venderemo mai le tue informazioni senza il tuo consenso.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content2:"Visualizza l'informativa sulla privacy di TikTok Shop per comprendere i tuoi diritti, i metodi di sicurezza dei dati e l'uso di qualsiasi informazione.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content3:"Ti serve aiuto? Il nostro centro assistenza virtuale all'interno dell'app TikTok \xe8 disponibile 24 ore su 24, 7 giorni su 7, e i nostri operatori online sono pronti ad assisterti durante l'orario di lavoro.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_learn_more:"Ulteriori informazioni",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_money_back_guarantee_content:"La nostra copertura \xe8 completamente gratuita e automatica sugli ordini idonei fino a 90 giorni, se l'articolo arriva danneggiato o difettoso. Si applicano limitazioni ed esclusioni.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_secure_payments_content5:"Per utilizzare una delle seguenti opzioni di pagamento, effettua l'acquisto all'interno dell'app:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_subtitle:"Ci impegniamo a offrirti un'ottima esperienza di acquisto.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle1:"Pagamenti sicuri",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle2:"Garanzia di rimborso",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle4:"Supporto in-app 24 su 24, 7 giorni su 7",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle5:"Privacy dei dati",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_title:"Protezioni TikTok Shop",tts_shop_returns_module_logged_out_content:"La maggior parte degli articoli sono idonei al <b>reso gratuito entro 30 giorni dalla consegna</b> per ottenere un rimborso. Alcuni articoli, tra cui prodotti alimentari, per l'igiene e articoli usati, non sono restituibili. Gli articoli in vendita finale non possono essere restituiti o sostituiti.",tts_shop_returns_module_title:"Resi semplificati",tts_shop_shipping_module_logged_out_co